# Fill these from your Supabase project: Settings -> API
# (Safe to ship in a desktop app — the anon key is public by design; RLS + the
#  Edge Function protect everything. Your ANTHROPIC key is NOT here — it's a
#  Supabase secret on the server.)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR-ANON-KEY
